oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 2519) for an order placed by the Nashville Symphony Orchestra for 35 one color window cards for a performance by the Nashville Symphony Orchestra at the Dickson High School Auditorium on April 29. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
